attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: This stunning 3-story townhouse in South Boston’s Westside-Seaport District, built in 2012, offers 1,845 sq ft of luxury living space. Features include oak flooring, a gas fireplace, surround sound, custom chef’s kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, wine cooler, and large center island. The master suite includes a private deck, walk-in closet, and a marble bath with dual sinks. Custom tile and marble bathrooms, crown molding, and custom closets throughout. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, garage parking, and a heated driveway.  Perfect for entertaining or relaxing, the home is just minutes from MBTA transit, parks, beaches, and South Boston’s vibrant restaurants and waterfront.
